news.title: Land for Evergrande's headquarters in Shenzhen put up for auction
news.para: The sale of the 10,000 square meter (2.47 acres)land will be held between Nov 21 to 26, according to the notice, which says the construction at the site have been halted since September 2021.

news.title: CM aims at making Odisha slum-free by 2023, launches land survey using drones
news.para: The land survey was taken in Bhubaneswar, Cuttack, Berhampur, Rourkela and Sambalpur civic body areas under the state government's 'Jaga Mission' programme.

news.title: Development of Noida airport on schedule, within budget: Top project officer
news.para: The greenfield airport is coming up in the Jewar area of western Uttar Pradesh's Gautam Buddh Nagar district, around 75 km from Delhi, and will be the second international airport in the National Capital Region (NCR).

news.title: With nine managing directors in eight years, Bhopal Metro project in slow lane
news.para: Unified Metropolitan Transport Authority for Bhopal metro is still awaited. It would lead to integration, planning and regulation of different commuting modes. Bhopal-based SPA has been roped in to cater to the influence area of the project.

news.title: Gurugram: Construction zone since 2019, no way to escape dust at Atul Kataria Chowk
news.para: It connects the city’s residents to Dwarka Expressway, the railway station, the bus stand, the Maruti manufacturing plant on the Old Palam Gurugram road, Kapashera border, Sheetla Mata temple, Signature Towers, and other residential and commercial hubs.

news.title: Chandigarh: Property tax not paid, five commercial buildings sealed
news.para: Out of the properties, two are shops and the rest commercial booths. “All these properties had to pay between Rs 20,000 to Rs 25,000 tax.

news.title: Only 21 lakh houses to be built for poor in Andhra Pradesh as against sanctioned 28.30 lakh
news.para: State Housing Minister J Ramesh said, "We have distributed 30.20 lakh house sites and are building 21 lakh houses in two phases. The programme will be completed by March 2024."

news.title: Redevelopment of old buildings in Nashik gain momentum
news.para: Last financial year, over 5,500 building plans for residential projects were submitted, of which 20% were related to redevelopment.

news.title: Karnataka: Master plan for development of Chamarajanagar town awaits government nod
news.para: The plan, drafted by the Chamarajanagar Urban Development Authority (Cuda), envisages the development of the border town in a phased manner.

news.title: Ajmera Realty posts net profit of Rs 34.18 crore in Q2 FY23
news.para: The company's net consolidated income stood at Rs 187.14 crore in Q2 FY23, a growth of 86.99 per cent from Rs 100.08 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Berger Paints posts net profit of Rs 219.51 crore in Q2 FY23
news.para: The company's net consolidated income stood at Rs 2,683.50 crore in Q2 FY23, a growth of 19.91 per cent from Rs 2,238 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Bengaluru: KSPCB fines Venkateshwara Builders for SWD buffer violation
news.para: The EC notice was issued as per the National Green Tribunal, Southern Zone, Chennai to Giri Babu GK and Mithun Gowda K of Venkateshwara Builders, Balaji Layout, Kaggadasapura in CV Raman Nagar.

news.title: Unauthorised construction bane to city's development: Delhi HC
news.para: The observation came while dismissing an appeal against an order of demolition of unauthorised construction carried out in a property in south Delhi's Hauz Khas.

news.title: Won't vacate homes without a compensation plan: Chintels Paradiso residents
news.para: An order by the district town planner to get two towers of Chintels Paradiso vacated at the earliest has left 42 families living there with an uncertain future.

news.title: Soon, MahaRERA valuers to check progress of projects
news.para: These valuers or inspectors would be certified by the income tax department or the Insolvency and Bankruptcy Board of India and carry out site visits.
